OL,3,CPumping station closure blamed as
OL,4,Chomes flooded
OL,6,FResidents of properties left flooded
OL,7,Fafter heavy rain say problems could
OL,8,Fhave been averted if a nearby pumping
OL,9,Fstation had not been shut down.
OL,11,FAbout 40 homes in Boston,
OL,12,FLincolnshire, were inundated with
OL,13,Fwater following bad weather on Monday
OL,14,Fand Tuesday as a major incident was
OL,15,Fdeclared.
OL,17,FHouseholders say there was little
OL,18,Fwarning before the South Forty Foot
OL,19,FDrain, also known as the Black Sluice
OL,20,FNavigation - the main drainage channel
OL,21,Fin the area - overflowed.
