OL,6,FIt came seven years after the Black
OL,7,FSluice Pumping Station was
OL,8,Fdecommissioned.
OL,10,FIan Pickering, who lives in the
OL,11,Fvillage of Wyberton, said that
OL,12,Fdecision had left the area vulnerable.
OL,14,FMr Pickering, who described himself as
OL,15,F"gutted and frozen", said: "They can
OL,16,Fempty that river in minutes with those
OL,17,Fpumps. I've witnessed it - they used
OL,18,Fto turn the pumps on, and the river
OL,19,Fwill go down to about 12 foot of water
OL,20,Fin the middle if they were working."
