OL,3,CPumping station closure blamed as
OL,4,Chomes flooded
OL,6,FFellow resident Kelly Sauny, who has
OL,7,F10 dogs, said she only knew she was
OL,8,Ffacing flooding when "the fire brigade
OL,9,Fwere hammering on my door".
OL,11,F"I came downstairs and the dogs were
OL,12,Fup to their shoulders in water," she
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"I've got a son who's got quite bad
OL,16,Fasthma so we can't be here, we've got
OL,17,Fno heating, we've got nothing. So I'm
OL,18,Fhaving to try and find kennels, but
OL,19,Fthat's expensive.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
