OL,3,CPumping station closure blamed as
OL,4,Chomes flooded
OL,6,F"None of us down the street have
OL,7,Fprocessed it."
OL,9,FCllr Paula Ashleigh-Morris, of Boston
OL,10,FBorough Council, called for the
OL,11,Fpumping station to be reopened. She
OL,12,Fsaid: "We felt that could have helped
OL,13,Fduring Storm Henk (in January 2024)
OL,14,Fbut it could certainly, it would seem,
OL,15,Fhave helped now and that's the
OL,16,Fprevalent view of every resident we've
OL,17,Fspoken to."
OL,19,FFellow councillor Tom Ashton added
OL,20,Fthere were "many questions" about the
OL,21,Fpumping station being decommissioned.
