OL,6,FIn a social media post he said: "I
OL,7,Fwill be expecting answers from the
OL,8,FEnvironment Agency as to what has gone
OL,9,Fwrong, and how they plan to keep local
OL,10,Fresidents safe in the future."
OL,12,FThe Environment Agency said there had
OL,13,Fbeen "record river levels" in the
OL,14,FSouth Forty Foot Drain after the snow
OL,15,Fand heavy rain.
