OL,3,CPumping station closure blamed as
OL,4,Chomes flooded
OL,6,FA spokesperson said the decision to
OL,7,Fclose the pumping station had been
OL,8,Fmade jointly by several organisations
OL,9,Fincluding the Black Sluice Internal
OL,10,FDrainage Board, Lincolnshire County
OL,11,FCouncil, Boston Borough Council and
OL,12,Fthe NFU.
OL,14,FThey added: "This decision was based
OL,15,Fon a four-year modelling study, which
OL,16,Fshowed that whilst the pumping station
OL,17,Fmakes a small difference to flood
OL,18,Frisk, this reduction in risk could not
OL,19,Foutweigh the cost of refurbishing and
OL,20,Frunning the asset for the future.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
